📊 Key Business Insights
The Top 5 exporting countries contribute 92.85% of total semiconductor trade value, indicating significant geographic concentration.
94.80% of semiconductor trade flows through only three trade routes, highlighting logistics dependency.
ASML is identified as the most strategically important supplier within the semiconductor ecosystem.
Taiwan combines substantial trade value with the highest geopolitical risk, making it a critical supply chain vulnerability.
DUV Lithography Machines represent the highest-value semiconductor technology segment in global trade.

